\newlabel{fig:ranking_shift}{{4}{6}{Per-task score matrix across 22 model configurations. Models (columns) × Tasks (rows). Green = high score, red = low score. The heatmap reveals distinct failure patterns: some models fail at early tasks (T1/T2) while others fail at later tasks (T4).\relax }{figure.caption.7}{}}
